
	This directory contains the following files:

	ccd.c		-	Main file for the utility "ccd"

	parddp.c	-	File containing code to parse "ddp"
				output. Part of "ccd" utility.

	parents.l	-	Pre-processes the ddp output file
				to extract information about parent
				classes. Part of "ccd" utility.

	mem.c		-	Memory management for efficiency.
				Part of "ccd" utility.

	ctd.l		-	Source code for the utility "ctd"

	showdict.c	-	Source code for the utility "showdict"

	srchdict.c	-	Source code for the utility "srchdict"
				(This is not a standard utility - just
				 to search for bitfields in a class instance).
